@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ziorkc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v0
    v0 = ((0.77 / wp.exp(tmp + 0.58)) + ((v0 + 0.50 * v0 + 0.44) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.40)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.96)) - 0.28)
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
